subsection.p:
So the algebra and the geometry say the same thing:

  \boxed{
  \begin{aligned}
  \amp\text{algebra: } d^2=0,\\[1mm]
  \amp\text{geometry: } \partial^2=0.
  \end{aligned}
  }
